flowchart TD
    title([Activity Diagram: Task Submission & Governance Flow])

    Start([🟢 Start: Agent Submits Task]) --> ValidateAuth

    ValidateAuth{Validate JWT Token}
    ValidateAuth -- Invalid --> AuthFail([❌ Return 401 Unauthorized])
    ValidateAuth -- Valid --> CheckAgent

    CheckAgent{Check Agent Status}
    CheckAgent -- SUSPENDED --> AgentFail([❌ Return 403 - Agent Suspended])
    CheckAgent -- ACTIVE --> CreateTask

    CreateTask[Create Task Record in DB\nstatus = PENDING] --> LogCreated
    LogCreated[Log TASK_CREATED in Audit Log] --> ExtractFeatures

    ExtractFeatures[Extract Task Feature Vector\ntask_type, input_data, agent_trust] --> RunML

    RunML[Run ML Anomaly Detection\nIsolation Forest + One-Class SVM] --> ScoreTask
    ScoreTask[Compute Ensemble Risk Score\n0.0 - 1.0] --> ClassifyRisk

    ClassifyRisk{Risk Level?}
    ClassifyRisk -- Score < 0.4 --> LowRisk[Set risk_level = LOW]
    ClassifyRisk -- 0.4–0.6 --> MedRisk[Set risk_level = MEDIUM]
    ClassifyRisk -- 0.6–0.8 --> HighRisk[Set risk_level = HIGH]
    ClassifyRisk -- Score > 0.8 --> CritRisk[Set risk_level = CRITICAL]

    LowRisk --> FetchRules
    MedRisk --> FetchRules
    HighRisk --> FetchRules
    CritRisk --> FetchRules

    FetchRules[Fetch Active Governance Rules\nOrdered by Priority DESC] --> EvalLoop

    EvalLoop{More Rules to Evaluate?}
    EvalLoop -- Yes --> CheckRule
    CheckRule{Rule Condition Matches Task?}
    CheckRule -- No --> EvalLoop
    CheckRule -- Yes --> LogTrigger

    LogTrigger[Log RULE_TRIGGERED in Audit Log] --> GetAction
    GetAction{Rule Action?}

    GetAction -- BLOCK --> BlockTask
    GetAction -- FLAG --> FlagTask
    GetAction -- REQUIRE_APPROVAL --> PendingApproval
    GetAction -- ALLOW --> EvalLoop
    GetAction -- LOG_ONLY --> EvalLoop
    GetAction -- ESCALATE --> EscalateTask

    BlockTask[Set status = BLOCKED] --> LogBlocked
    LogBlocked[Log TASK_BLOCKED] --> ReturnBlocked([🔴 Return BLOCKED to caller])

    FlagTask[Set status = FLAGGED] --> LogFlagged
    LogFlagged[Log TASK_FLAGGED] --> ReturnFlagged([🟡 Return FLAGGED - Awaiting Review])

    PendingApproval[Set status = PENDING_APPROVAL] --> NotifyManager
    NotifyManager[Notify Manager for Manual Review] --> ReturnPending([🟡 Return PENDING_APPROVAL])

    EscalateTask[Create Escalation Record] --> NotifyAdmin
    NotifyAdmin[Notify Admin] --> LogEscalate[Log ESCALATION_CREATED] --> ReturnEscalated([🟡 Return ESCALATED])

    EvalLoop -- No more rules --> ApproveTask
    ApproveTask[Set status = APPROVED] --> LogApproved
    LogApproved[Log TASK_APPROVED] --> ExecuteTask

    ExecuteTask[Execute Task\nRecord start_time] --> TaskRunning{Task Execution}
    TaskRunning -- Success --> CompleteTask
    TaskRunning -- Failure --> FailTask

    CompleteTask[Set status = COMPLETED\nRecord execution_time_ms] --> LogComplete
    LogComplete[Log TASK_COMPLETED] --> End1([🟢 End: Task Complete])

    FailTask[Set status = FAILED\nRecord error] --> LogFail
    LogFail[Log TASK_FAILED] --> End2([🔴 End: Task Failed])

    style Start fill:#4caf50,color:#fff
    style AuthFail fill:#f44336,color:#fff
    style AgentFail fill:#f44336,color:#fff
    style ReturnBlocked fill:#f44336,color:#fff
    style ReturnFlagged fill:#ff9800,color:#fff
    style ReturnPending fill:#ff9800,color:#fff
    style ReturnEscalated fill:#ff9800,color:#fff
    style End1 fill:#4caf50,color:#fff
    style End2 fill:#f44336,color:#fff
